    "They generate compliance manuals and audit reports (i.e., Suspicious Activity Reports) and publish legal advisories.",
    "While many compliance documents remain internal, some client advisories and industry guidelines are publicly available.",
    "A.2.3 Where \"Where was the data generated/annotated?\"",
    "In finance, textual data arises from multiple channels.",
    "Corporate disclosures are uploaded to regulatory databases (e.g., the SEC's Electronic Data Gathering, Analysis, and Retrieval (EDGAR)), press releases appear on news-wires or company websites, and social media data is generated globally."
